deck: The story of Rest is finally gathered together in one volume! The premise of this world is that there is a drug out there that will allow you to stay awake 24/7 and has no side effects. However, when something seems too good to be true, it usually is.
description:
Written by Mark Powers (GI Joe), art by Shawn McManus (Sandman) and Marco Castiello (Witchblade) and covers by the industry's hottest talents including Tim Sale (Heroes), Phil Jimenez (Amazing Spider-man) and others.

The story of Rest is finally gathered together in one volume! The premise of this world is that there is a drug out there that will allow you to stay awake 24/7 and has no side effects. However, when something seems too good to be true, it usually is. With issues 0-5 as well as bonus materials included, this trade paperback is sure to satisfy the needs of any fan and is also a great introduction to the universe for new fans.
name: Rest

description:
Eight-issue limited series about an alternate history in which England had to fight a war against zombies in the 19th century and only won by turning most Englishmen into vampires that couldn't be killed. The story is set long after the war and begins when several people are found dead. Since no one is supposed to die anymore, Inspector George Suttle, a former war veteran, investigates the murders and finds many dark spots in this bright new world.

By Dan Abnett and I.N.J. Culbard, published by Vertigo in 2012.

Collected in The New Deadwardians.
name: The New Deadwardians

description:
It's no longer coming, it's here! Does the return of the Phoenix on Earth signal the rebirth of the mutant species or the end of life as know it? And when the Avengers and X-Men end up on opposing sides, it means war. The series was continued in the AVX: Consequences mini-series.

This is the first Marvel series that uses the AR Scanner, unfolding new scenes or information by scanning an "AR" marked page within the comic with the AR Scanner on your smartphone. Through the printed copy's Marvel also offered a special code that unlocked the Avengers Vs. X-Men: Infinite comics.

Collected Editions

  • Avengers Vs. X-Men HC (#0-12)
  • Avengers Vs X-Men TPB (#0-12)

Translated into Brazilian, French, German & Spanish.
name: Avengers Vs. X-Men
